          <IonButtons slot="end">
            <IonButton routerLink="/general">General</IonButton>
            <IonButton routerLink="/attack">Attack</IonButton>
            <IonButton routerLink="/defence">DÃ©fence</IonButton>
          </IonButtons>
        </IonToolbar>

    </IonPage>
  </IonApp>
);

export default NavBar;
